{"tid":900270,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好辛苦，很想幫你。。 但係你唔畀","createTime":"2018-11-13T06:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T06:11:42.000Z","uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"38dc9a740094c538050b0d33527865ee3b326ce3","tid":900270,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:08:19.000Z","msg":"很想幫你撩鼻屎阿阿阿阿阿阿阿阿阿阿阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\nd鼻屎大粒到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n圖如果幫佢撩到既話就後補！！！"},{"pid":"edae76d92b5ed1d582b652b84d71b146c34c7889","tid":900270,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:10:49.000Z","msg":"睇住示意圖先啦大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.gyazo.com/7e31f474571e8725b0bb5ff057e45cfe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F7e31f474571e8725b0bb5ff057e45cfe.gif&h=6f464eb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45b41e77fea115ddcc42a9e09c68591b2f67c116","tid":900270,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:11:42.000Z","msg":"「鼻屎」是由鼻黏膜分泌的鼻水，混合空氣的塵埃或微生物等變乾而成。挖鼻後把鼻屎隨處「飛彈」固然是不衛生行為，家長都會千方百計阻止小孩手多多，或把自己挖出的鼻屎放到口中。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;　鼻水能防止蛀牙　吞下能增強免疫力<br />\n不過，近日有專家發現這個吃「鼻屎」的行為很可能是來自祖先的本能行為，而且有益無害。一群來自麻省理工學院（Massachusetts Institute of Technology，MIT）與哈佛大學（Harvard University）的研究學者，在最一期《美國微生物學會期刊》（American Society for Microbiology Journal）中發表文章，指出「吃鼻屎有益健康」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n研究發現「鼻屎」能預防呼吸道感染，對抗愛滋病病毒，鼻屎附帶的鼻水亦可阻止細菌黏附在牙齒上造成蛀牙，而吞下鼻水甚至有預防胃潰瘍的功效。有研究正嘗試分離「鼻屎」中的有益成份，製成牙膏或香口膠，用作防止蛀牙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n研究人員亦指出，由於鼻屎本身因混有細菌，當進入消化道就能啟動免疫系統發揮作用，增進腸道健康。"}]}